snippet.title: Chronicle of Infinity | Fighter Class - Dragoon
snippet.description:
The Heir of Titan.

Dragoon Corps have unparalleled courage and strength. They  can cope with each dangerous situation with "Dragon Slaughter Gun" .  They like to add Dragon Crystal and other dragon elements to their equipment to match their powerful titles of Dragoon Warrior.
